# Cursor Rules (AI Agent Guidelines)

Any AI developer agent operating in this workspace must read and strictly follow the state guidelines and constraints defined in:
1. `intent_engine/AI_INSTRUCTIONS.md`
2. `intent_engine/INTENT.md`

## Setup Configuration
* Read `intent_engine/deepsleep/logs/` at startup to load the persistent state.
* If a request is ambiguous, stop execution and present clarifying questions as defined in `intent_engine/waking/clarification_template.md`.
* Compile draft codes only under `intent_engine/dreaming/sandbox/`.
* Log decisions and files under `intent_engine/deepsleep/`.
